description: There's nothing like a fresh picked Georgia peach, and nobody brings them to you fresher than The Peach Truck. The best peaches on Earth grow from Georgia soil, and the peaches plucked from Pearson farms are the greatest you'll ever find. Whether off the side of the road or brought straight to your door, The Peach Truck is providing the greatest taste on Earth to you!
name: The Peach Truck
